{
  "stem": "19502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, well-- well, it was the age difference of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- I always wished I had someone younger than myself where I could boss them also around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very much bossed around by my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, all the same, my parents stood up for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- [CRYING] it was a happy life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father worked in the forest, see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- I don't know how you call it in here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was an estimator.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he looked at the-- at a tree, at any kind of certain tree, he could tell how much two-- how many two-by-fours would come out, if it's a healthy tree or if it's not a healthy-- how much wood it'll come out.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- it came by the meters, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was-- and we dealt in forestry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was dealing with forestries because, I mean, you didn't own-- that-- that probably was leased.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every year when-- when it was the finish of the season, you know, when they used to cut down the-- the trees, cut down the trees, they used to sell it with the sloops by the river into Poland.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Probably from there went somewhere else, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a very, very big celebration when it was the end of the season.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a saw mill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather had one, but then later it was-- it burned down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, there were people were working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were cut down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a Lesnik.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was one that looks after, you know, like-- like a forest ranger, you know, takes care of all the things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it used to go they cut them down and then bring them to the river.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
